/API/Document/dragleave_event\"><code>dragleave</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragover_event\"><code>dragover</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/dragstart_event\"><code>dragstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/drop_event\"><code>drop</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/fullscreenchange_event\"><code>fullscreenchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/fullscreenerror_event\"><code>fullscreenerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/gotpointercapture_event\"><code>gotpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/lostpointercapture_event\"><code>lostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/mssitemodejumplistitemremoved_event\"><code>mssitemodejumplistitemremoved</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/msthumbnailclick_event\"><code>msthumbnailclick</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointercancel_event\"><code>pointercancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerdown_event\"><code>pointerdown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerenter_event\"><code>pointerenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerleave_event\"><code>pointerleave</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerlockchange_event\"><code>pointerlockchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerlockerror_event\"><code>pointerlockerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointermove_event\"><code>pointermove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerout_event\"><code>pointerout</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerover_event\"><code>pointerover</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/pointerup_event\"><code>pointerup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document/readystatechange_event\"><code>readystatechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">O método&nbsp;<code><strong>Document.hasFocus()</strong></code>&nbsp;retorna um valor&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> que indica se&nbsp;o documento ou qualquer&nbsp;elemento dentro do&nbsp;documento está com o foco ativo. Este método pode ser usado para determinar se o elemento ativo em um documento tem foco.</div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p>Quando se está visualizando um documento, um elemento com focus é sempre o ativo no mesmo, mas um elemento ativo&nbsp;não necessariamente&nbsp;tem o foco. Por exemplo, um elemento ativo com uma janela&nbsp;(popup) que não é a principal não tem foco.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">focused = document.hasFocus();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_retornado","title":"Valor retornado","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>false</code>&nbsp;se o elemento ativo no documento não&nbsp;tem foco; <code>true</code> se o elemento ativo no documento tem foco.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html;highlight:[17] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>en<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>meta</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">charset</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>UTF-8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>TEST<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">#message</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n<span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> checkPageFocus<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">checkPageFocus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> info <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hasFocus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"O documento tem o foco.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    info<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"O documento não tem o foco.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">openWindow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">open</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"http://developer.mozilla.org/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"mozdev\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    \"width<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">640</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    height<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    left<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">150</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    top<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">260</span>\"\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Exemplo do JavaScript hasFocus<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>message<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Esperando por ação do usuário<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value javascript language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">openWindow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Abre uma nova janela<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type